&lt;p&gt;
	The Cribs - Another Number&lt;br /&gt;
	This song made it obvious to me that you can create very simple songs and anchor the whole thing to a simple theme. Keep the theme short and running and you&amp;#39;ll have a memorable song.&lt;/p&gt;
